<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gam khat sun sanga vak zaw a um,
 Ginnan gal apat in I mu thei;
 I zawt lai hin I Pau in ei ngak,
 I chenna diu mun siem din A um.

[V2]
 Dan leh kipak takin,
 Luigal hawih achun kituok hitiu;
 Dan leh kipak takin,
 Luigal hawih achun kituok hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Zie luigal hawih achun lasa'i tiu,
 Nun nuoma umte la hawihtak chuh
 I thagau uh lungkham ta puo'n a,
 Chawlhna nuom ngaiin tau ta puoi tiu.

[V4]
 3. Vana I Pau bangcheng nei kawmah,
 Chawihat na lopi tak chuh piei tiu;
 A hehpihna lopi tak ziek leh,
 Damsung vangsakna ei piek ziekin.</lyrics>
<title>SWEET BY AND BY</title>
<hymn_number>366</hymn_number>
</song>